      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Aug 2 article about antibiotic-resistant bacteria regarding spelling of species of bacteria cited in article (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Aug. 2 about bacteria that are resistant to antibiotics misspelled the name of a species of bacteria. It is Staphylococcus aureus, not staphylococcus aureas.</p>
      </block>
